original_title: Van Der Graaf Generator - Live At Rockpalast - Leverkusen 2005
overview: Recorded live on November 5th, 2005 at the Leverkusener Jazztage at the Forum Leverkusen, Leverkusen, Germany. Setlist includes: Darkness, -Interview-, The Sleep Walkers, Every Bloody Emperor, -Interview-, Man Erg, Killer and Lemmings.
title: Van Der Graaf Generator - Live At Rockpalast - Leverkusen 2005
